    "title": "Industrial Floor Coatings for Auto Service Areas",
    "content": "Auto Service Areas\nAutomotive service areas require ultra-durable floors not only resistant to impact and heavy abrasion, but also chemical and stain resistance to common petrochemicals. Our flooring systems bring these benefits together along with increased slip resistance even when wet. Optional line striping and customization adds additional aesthetic appeal and branding.\nAdvantages\nResistant to damage from water, de-icing salt, and petrochemicals\nImpact and abrasion resistant\nSlip resistant in wet or dry conditions for pedestrian and vehicular safety\nQuick install, minimal downtime\nSuitable for high automobile traffic and other heavy machinery\nEasy to maintain\nOptions for line striping, directional arrows and safety markings\nFor new construction and existing surfaces in need of repair and/or protection\nSuitable for extreme hot and cold environments\nExtreme temperature resistances including freeze/thaw conditions and extreme heat\nCustom colors to match company colors, logos and branding themes\nService departments\nMaintenance shops\nBody shops and detailing centers\nGarages\nWarehouses\nParamount\nUrethane Cement",
